            , was indicted for <rs id="t17280717-14-off58" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17280717-14-off58" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17280717-14-off58" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing four Perukes, two Razors, and five Ounces of Humane Hair, the Goods of 
                     <persName id="t17280717-14-victim78" type="victimName">
                        Moses 
                        Freeman 
                     <interp inst="t17280717-14-victim78" type="surname" value="Freeman"></interp>
